CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 15, 1966, pg.1B reads:"60Th Anniversary Tea - After the interesting program celebrating the 60th anniversary fo the Violet Art Club at St. James AME Church, the photographer got this picture of some of the ladies grouped around the tea table. Left to right; Mmes. Rosetta McKinney, Gertrude B. Smith, L. Owens, Camellia Morgan, Barbara Bush, club presidetn; Risie Lewis, Mary Hall, Elaine Miller, Edith Blackman and Sedonia Pettigrew."
TitMainTitle: Ten women, from left: Rosetta McKinney, Gertrude B. Smith, L. Owens, Camellia Morgan, Barbara Bush, Risie Lewis, Mary Hall, Elaine Miller, Edith Blackman, and Sedonia Pettigrew, gathered in St. James AME Church for Violet Art Club sixtieth anniversary tea
